Why AGPL-3.0?

The AGPL-3.0 ensures that improvements and modifications to this software
remain open-source and benefit the entire community. This is particularly
important for web-based software like Beanflow Payroll, as it prevents
the software from being used in proprietary services without contributing
improvements back to the community.

For more information, visit: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html
